SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK b1.
PARAMETERS p_cat(1)  TYPE c.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK b1.


START-OF-SELECTION.
 CASE p_cat.
 WHEN 'A'.
 WRITE: 'moto'.
 WHEN 'B'.
 WRITE: ' carro' .
 WHEN 'C'.
 WRITE: ' Veiculos de carga'.
 WHEN 'D'.
 WRITE: ' Transporte de passageiros'.
 WHEN 'E'.
 WRITE: 'Caminhoes'.
 WHEN OTHERS.
 WRITE 'Categoria invalida'.
ENDCASE.
